sky.tennis.uk.title: ATP Toronto 2025 Review
sky.tennis.uk.description: A review of the 2025 Canadian Open, an ATP Masters 1000 hard-court event held in Toronto.

sky.tennis.uk.title: WTA Final: Beijing
sky.tennis.uk.description: A women's singles champion is crowned in the final of the China Open - a WTA 1000 event. (05.10)

sky.tennis.uk.title: WTA Final: Wuhan
sky.tennis.uk.description: Coco Gauff awaits compatriot Jessica Pegula, fresh from ending Aryna Sabalenka's 20-match winning run, in an all-American Wuhan final. The pair meet in their first final together. (12.10)

sky.tennis.uk.title: WTA Final: Cincinnati
sky.tennis.uk.description: Six-time Grand Slam champion Iga Swiatek faces Jasmine Paolini for the Cincinnati title. In what will be Swiatek's 13th WTA 1000 final, Paolini is competing in just her third. (18.08)

sky.tennis.uk.title: WTA Final: Seoul
sky.tennis.uk.description: Iga Swiatek enters her first Korea Open final as the 24-year-old Pole meets Ekaterina Alexandrova as the top two seeds vie for the WTA 500 title in Seoul. (21.09)

sky.tennis.uk.title: Billie Jean King: My Story
sky.tennis.uk.description: Billie Jean King discusses her life story, including her ongoing fight for equality and the victories on and off the court that have shaped her into the legend she is today.

sky.tennis.uk.title: ATP Final: Vienna
sky.tennis.uk.description: In a rematch of the Australian Open final, Jannik Sinner and Alexander Zverev meet in Vienna. Sinner, appearing in his eighth final of 2025, bids to deny Zverev a second title here. (26.10)

sky.tennis.uk.title: ATP Final: Paris
sky.tennis.uk.description: A year-end champion is crowned in the French capital at the Rolex Paris Masters. (02.11)

sky.tennis.uk.title: ATP Finals: Turin Final
sky.tennis.uk.description: World number one Carlos Alcaraz faces Italy's reigning ATP Finals champion Jannik Sinner in their sixth meeting of the year, marking the finale to the 2025 Tour season in Turin. (16.11)

sky.f1.uk.title: Abu Dhabi F1 Grand Prix
sky.f1.uk.description: It's lights out for the title decider. Starting behind polesitter Max Verstappen, Lando Norris will become world champion with a podium. Oscar Piastri has it all to do from third. (07.12)

sky.f1.uk.title: Ted's Notebook: Abu Dhabi

sky.f1.uk.title: The Rise Of MVG (2013)

sky.f1.uk.title: Gary Anderson: Back2Back Champion
sky.f1.uk.description: Gary Anderson tells the story of his PDC World Darts Championship triumphs in 2015 and 2016, as the Scotsman become only the third player to win back-to-back titles. Ep 6.

sky.f1.uk.title: 30 Years of the PDC World Champs'
sky.f1.uk.description: In celebration of 30 years of the PDC World Darts Championship, take a look back at the very first tournament, a classic final from 2007 and one of the greatest legs ever played. Ep 1.

sky.f1.uk.title: The Greatest Final 07:Taylor v RVB
sky.f1.uk.description: In the final act at the Circus Tavern, two of the finest players to have ever played the sport created a match for the ages, as Phil Taylor and Raymond van Barneveld met in the final. Ep 3.

sky.f1.uk.title: Darts Gold: Taylor v Barneveld
sky.f1.uk.description: A chance to relive classic darts matches. Here is Phil Taylor against Raymond van Barneveld in the semi-finals of the 2013 PDC World Darts Championship at London's Alexandra Palace.

sky.f1.uk.title: World Darts Championship Final '21
sky.f1.uk.description: The curtain closes on darts' biggest event with the final of the 2021 PDC World Darts Championship at the Alexandra Palace. Here, Gerwyn Price and Gary Anderson go head to head.

sky.f1.uk.title: World Darts Championship Final '22
sky.f1.uk.description: Michael Smith and Peter Wright meet as the two standout players in the final of 2022 World Darts Championship. Will it be 'Bully Boy' or 'Snakebite' who wins the Sid Waddell Trophy?

sky.f1.uk.title: World Darts Championship Final '23
sky.f1.uk.description: Michael van Gerwen and Michael Smith clash in the final of the 2022/23 World Darts Championship at Alexandra Palace. MVG targets a fourth title, while Smith eyes his maiden win. (03.01)

sky.f1.uk.title: World Darts Championship Final '24
sky.f1.uk.description: The eyes of a nation were fixed on the Ally Pally stage as one of the great sporting stories, told by Luke Littler and Luke Humphries, concluded during the World Darts Championship final.

sky.f1.uk.title: World Darts Championship Final '25
sky.f1.uk.description: Luke Littler competes in a second consecutive World Darts Championship final, as the 17-year-old wonderkid takes on three-time champion Michael van Gerwen at Alexandra Palace. (03.01)

sky.f1.uk.title: Rob & Romesh Vs Darts

sky.f1.uk.title: WDC Final 2025: Littler v van Gerwen

sky.f1.uk.title: World Darts Championship Final '25
